					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-516607#post-1497106</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-516607/scp-1560#post-1497106</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 03 Jul 2012 01:32:59 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Khym Chanur</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>163438</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>SCP-1560 's eyes differ greatly from that of terrestrial avians, being a compound eye that has been proven to be highly sensitive to ultraviolet wavelengths as a result of Foundation testing.</p> </blockquote> <p>&quot; as a result of Foundation testing&quot; is unneeded, and kind of makes it sound like the Foundation testing <em>caused</em> them to be sensitive to ultraviolet light.</p> <blockquote> <p>SCP-1560-21 reappeared during a hunting &quot;dive&quot; on ██/██/██ and reappeared badly wounded.</p> </blockquote> <p>I think that should be &quot;SCP-1560-21 disappeared during&quot;.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-516607#post-1497102</guid>
