				<wikidot:authorName>Hurtz</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1328710</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Kind of an offbeat oddity.</p> <p>Quick question:</p> <blockquote> <p>SCP-1560 's eyes differ greatly from that of terrestrial avians, being a compound eye that has been proven to be highly sensitive to ultraviolet wavelengths as a result of Foundation testing.</p> </blockquote> <p>I think what you're trying to say is that Foundation experiments have determined that their eyes are sensitive to UV wavelengths, but the first time I read it it came across as their eyes are sensitive to UV waves as a result of Foundation testing.</p> <p>Is my reread accurate?</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
